QUESTION : You are given an array of integers arr[]. Your task is to reverse the given array. (JAVA)

SOLUTION : 
class Solution{
  public void reverseArray(int arr[]){
    int left = 0;
    int right = arr.length-1;

    #reverse the array in place
    while(left<right){
      int temp = arr[left];
      arr[left] = arr[right];
      arr[right] = temp;
      left++;
      right--;
    }
  }
}
